## Coursera: Introduction to Python Programming

The [Introduction to Python Programming](https://www.coursera.org/learn/python-programming-intro) course is part of the [Introduction to Programming with Python and Java Specialization](https://www.coursera.org/specializations/programming-python-java). 

* **Module 1: Course Introduction, Intro to Programming and The Python Language, Variables, Conditionals, Jupyter Notebook, and IDLE**
* **Module 2: Intro to Lists, Loops, and Functions**
* **Module 3: More with Lists, Strings, Tuples, Sets, and PyCharm**
* **Module 4: Dictionaries and Files**
